to create db:
flask --app run.py db init
flask --app run.py db migrate -m "Initial schema - all models"
flask --app run.py db upgrade

it may give error. i think only upgrade command fill do, since i commit migrations folder too.
idk. ask chatgpt if you have problem. camt help with that.

make sure u have instance folder. and after this it will create
meetingpoint.db. with 7 tables.


